### GET `/messages`
#### Endpoint
- Method: `GET`
- Full path: `/messages`
- Function: `MessagesController.findAll`

#### Description
Return paginated message logs with optional filtering by message status.

#### Request
- Params: none
- Query:
  - `status`: `MessageStatus`, optional, one of `SENT | FAILED | RECALL`
  - `page`: `number`, optional, default `1`
  - `limit`: `number`, optional, default `20`
- Body: none

Example request:

```json
{
  "status": "SENT",
  "page": 1,
  "limit": 20
}
```

#### Response

```json
{
  "data": [
    {
      "id": "1f0b96fc-c694-4d83-8f4c-20fa20aa0001",
      "messageZaloId": "987654321",
      "cliMsgId": "1713171000000",
      "uidFrom": "1122334455",
      "content": "Hello group",
      "senderId": "7c13f32f-90eb-483f-b5e0-c3b7fa120002",
      "groupId": "5d6a8d48-b45c-43d8-9b0d-5cc3bd110001",
      "sentAt": "2026-04-15T09:00:00.000Z",
      "status": "SENT",
      "createdAt": "2026-04-15T09:00:00.000Z",
      "sender": {
        "id": "7c13f32f-90eb-483f-b5e0-c3b7fa120002",
        "zaloId": "1122334455",
        "name": "Child Account",
        "phone": "0909999999"
      },
      "group": {
        "id": "5d6a8d48-b45c-43d8-9b0d-5cc3bd110001",
        "groupName": "Marketing Team",
        "groupZaloId": "1234567890123456789"
      }
    }
  ],
  "meta": {
    "page": 1,
    "limit": 20,
    "total": 1,
    "totalPages": 1
  }
}
```

#### Error cases
- `400`: invalid query validation
- `401`: missing/invalid JWT
- `500`: unexpected server error

#### Authentication
- JWT required
- Guards: `JwtAuthGuard`
- Roles: any authenticated `ADMIN` or `USER`

### POST `/messages/send`
#### Endpoint
- Method: `POST`
- Full path: `/messages/send`
- Function: `MessagesController.send`

#### Description
Send a message to a stored Zalo group using the child account with the lowest group count under the selected master account.

#### Request
- Params: none
- Query: none
- Body:
  - `masterId`: `string`, required
  - `groupId`: `string`, required
  - `content`: `string`, required

Example request:

```json
{
  "masterId": "7c13f32f-90eb-483f-b5e0-c3b7fa120001",
  "groupId": "5d6a8d48-b45c-43d8-9b0d-5cc3bd110001",
  "content": "Hello group"
}
```

#### Response

```json
{
  "id": "1f0b96fc-c694-4d83-8f4c-20fa20aa0001",
  "messageZaloId": "987654321",
  "cliMsgId": "1713171000000",
  "uidFrom": "1122334455",
  "content": "Hello group",
  "senderId": "7c13f32f-90eb-483f-b5e0-c3b7fa120002",
  "groupId": "5d6a8d48-b45c-43d8-9b0d-5cc3bd110001",
  "sentAt": "2026-04-15T09:00:00.000Z",
  "status": "SENT",
  "createdAt": "2026-04-15T09:00:00.000Z",
  "sender": {
    "id": "7c13f32f-90eb-483f-b5e0-c3b7fa120002",
    "zaloId": "1122334455",
    "name": "Child Account",
    "phone": "0909999999"
  },
  "group": {
    "id": "5d6a8d48-b45c-43d8-9b0d-5cc3bd110001",
    "groupName": "Marketing Team",
    "groupZaloId": "1234567890123456789"
  }
}
```

#### Error cases
- `400`: validation error
- `400`: selected master is not a master account
- `400`: no active child Zalo session
- `400`: selected child account is missing `zaloId`
- `400`: anti-spam interval violation
- `400`: message interval configuration missing/invalid
- `400`: Zalo send or group-join failure
- `401`: missing/invalid JWT
- `404`: master account not found
- `404`: group not found
- `500`: unexpected server error

#### Authentication
- JWT required
- Guards: `JwtAuthGuard`
- Roles: any authenticated `ADMIN` or `USER`

### POST `/messages/recall/:id`
#### Endpoint
- Method: `POST`
- Full path: `/messages/recall/:id`
- Function: `MessagesController.recall`

#### Description
Recall a previously sent message using Zalo undo API, then mark the stored message status as `RECALL`.

#### Request
- Params:
  - `id`: `string`, UUID
- Query: none
- Body: none

#### Response
If message is already recalled:

```json
{
  "id": "1f0b96fc-c694-4d83-8f4c-20fa20aa0001",
  "status": "RECALL"
}
```

If recall succeeds now:

```json
{
  "id": "1f0b96fc-c694-4d83-8f4c-20fa20aa0001",
  "messageZaloId": "987654321",
  "cliMsgId": "1713171000000",
  "uidFrom": "1122334455",
  "content": "Hello group",
  "senderId": "7c13f32f-90eb-483f-b5e0-c3b7fa120002",
  "groupId": "5d6a8d48-b45c-43d8-9b0d-5cc3bd110001",
  "sentAt": "2026-04-15T09:00:00.000Z",
  "status": "RECALL",
  "createdAt": "2026-04-15T09:00:00.000Z",
  "undoStatus": 0
}
```

#### Error cases
- `400`: invalid UUID
- `400`: only `SENT` messages can be recalled
- `400`: stored recall data is incomplete
- `400`: upstream Zalo undo/session failure
- `401`: missing/invalid JWT
- `404`: message not found
- `500`: unexpected server error

#### Authentication
- JWT required
- Guards: `JwtAuthGuard`
- Roles: any authenticated `ADMIN` or `USER`

## Configs API
